Titolo: Earth 2150: Lost Souls

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Earth 2150: Lost Souls is the second sequel to the real time strategy game Earth 2150. 
While it is a stand-alone game, many consider it the second expansion pack because it does little more than provide new missions, and weapons. The story takes place alongside the original game's story. Lost Souls was released in 2002.

Genere: Strategy 

Valutazione: N/A
